Potato cactus is a Farming plant grown at level 64 Farming. A potato cactus can be grown by planting a potato cactus seed in a cactus patch found in Al Kharid or the Farming Guild. Growth time is approximately 70 minutes. Players can harvest potato cacti from the mature plant.

A nearby gardener will watch over your growing potato cactus plant in exchange for 8 snape grass.

'''Potato cactus''' is a [[Farming]] plant grown at level 64 Farming. A potato cactus can be grown by planting a [[potato cactus seed]] in a [[cactus patch]] found in [[Al Kharid]] or the [[Farming Guild]]. Growth time is approximately 70 minutes. Players can harvest [[potato cactus|potato cacti]] from the mature plant.

A nearby gardener will watch over your growing potato cactus plant in exchange for 8 [[snape grass]].
